Wruq6JnXZto.title: SweetFX enabled in - Dead Rising 3 - gameplay PC [Win 8.1][ Improved graphics mod ]
Wruq6JnXZto.description:
Dead Rising 3 - zombi game is now visually enhanced with SweetFX preset. SweetFX works on Windows 7 / 8 / 8.1 - for both Nvidia and Amd cards!!!

Dead Rising 3 purchase link: http://unavailable/1MZQ8hg

You need to use Radeonpro with the presets. Guide is in here - 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9X1CrTYyV7o

Preset - https://www.sendspace.com/file/9xem9t
 
Join in GAMING & BENCHMARKS & SweetFX mods community-https://plus.google.com/b/109742001994795218567/communities/110598602590445579038

Follow on Twitter - https://twitter.com/multitechnopark

Like on Facebook - MultiTechnopark - GAMERS HEAVEN
https://www.facebook.com/pages/MultiTechnopark-GAMERS-HEAVEN/611017988934562?fref=ts

So in case you're new to SweetFX Shader Suite (or just SweetFX), it's a mod built on the InjectSMAA shader injector, that allows you to apply a suite of post processing shader effects to your games.
You can add SMAA anti-aliasing , sharpening and tweak the color, gamma , exposure and more.
It's meant to allow you to improve the look of your games and change the look and mood of it to your liking.
If you use SMAA antialiasing instead of MSAA or an even more expensive antialaliasing technique you can also make the game run faster (than with MSAA)

Compatibility

It works with all graphics cards as long as they support at least shader model 3. That's all cards produced after 2002 (give or take).
It does not work with 64bit game executables yet, however 64bit support should be coming in the near future - so far use the 32bit version of your game if it gives you a choice between 32 and 64bit.
It should work on Windows 2000 and newer, both 32bit and 64bit. So far tested working on WinXP , Vista , Win7 and Windows 8.
It may work on Linux using Wine - please report your findings.
It does not work well with most programs that overlay an image onto the game. It has a workaround for the Steam overlay so that will work, and you can make overlays based on Rivatuner OSD work as well with a compability setting in those overlays , but other overlays may prevent SweetFX from making changes to the image or outright crash the game - turn those off.
SweetFX is a universal image improvement and tweaking mod,
that works with almost any 32bit (and hopefully soon 64bit) DirectX 9, 10 or 11 game or application.

It's goal is provide similar tools to games in realtime, as video processing software provides for movies and videos.

Effects included:

* SMAA Anti-aliasing : Anti-aliases the image using the SMAA technique - see http://www.iryoku.com/smaa/
* FXAA Anti-aliasing : Anti-aliases the image using the FXAA technique - currently only work under DirectX9. Use the d3d9.dll found in \SweetFX\dlls\FXAA DX9 dll\ for this.
* Explosion : Scatters the pixels similarly to the Explosion filter in Irfanview
* Cartoon : Creates an outline-effect that makes the image look more cartoonish.
* Advanced CRT : Mimics the look of an old arcade CRT display.
* LumaSharpen : Sharpens the image, making details easier to see
* Bloom : Makes strong lights bleed their light into their surroundings
* HDR : Mimics an HDR tonemapped look
* Levels : Sets a new black and white point. A fast and easy way to increase contrast but it causes clipping. The Curves effect does this in a more subtle way without causing clipping.
* Technicolor : Makes the image look like it was processed using a three-strip Technicolor process - see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technicolor
* Cineon DPX : Makes the image look like it was converted from film to Cineon DPX. Can be used to create a "sunny" look.
* Monochrome : Removes colors from the image so it appears as if shot on black and white film.
* Lift Gamma Gain : Adjust brightness and color of shadows, midtones and highlights (and typically does it better then the Tonemap effect)
* Tonemap : Adjust gamma, exposure, saturation, bleach and defog. (may cause clipping)
* Vibrance : Intelligently saturates (or desaturates if you use negative values) the pixels depending on their original saturation.
* Curves : Contrast adjustments using S-curves - without causing clipping.
* Sepia : Sepia tones the image - see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sepia_tone#Sepia_toning

b__Q_9GY79k.title: Фестиваль танцев на льду 2010 "Чтобы помнили..." (Часть2)
b__Q_9GY79k.description: Детский театр на льду «Алеко» организован в 1977 г. профсоюзным комитетом автомобильного завода имени Ленинского комсомола (АЗЛК). В 1989 г. театру присвоено звание «Образцовый художественный коллектив». В первый тренерско-педагогический состав театра входили: художественный руководитель -- заслуженная артистка РСФСР Самсонова Н.М., хореограф -- Сафонова О.В., тренеры-педагоги, мастера спорта СССР -- Карпова Е.Н., Барскова О.Л., Галкина М.О., Варьяш Н.П.. С 1998 г. художественный руководитель и режиссер-постановщик театра Кондрашова Ольга Ильинична. Свою творческую жизнь детский театр начал с композиций -- «Пусть всегда будет солнце!», «Неуловимые», «Широка страна моя родная!», «Время вперед!». Позже в репертуаре театра появились балеты «Айболит» и «Щелкунчик», концертная программа «Я иду, шагаю по Москве». Коллектив театра участвовал в художественной программе Московских Олимпийских игр, XII международного фестиваля молодежи и студентов, международных соревнований «Московские новости». В дни зимних школьных каникул театр радует маленьких москвичей красочными новогодними представлениями.

4SC3iif84F8.title: Snake Island
4SC3iif84F8.description:
In this Ben Cropp production we are taken to Niue; the beautiful, uplifted atoll situated in the Central Pacific, 4000km north of Australia. Honeycombed with limestone caves, Niue is a speck of land in a vast ocean of sea snakes and humpback whales.

We join Cropp as he explores both the islands colourful wildlife, and the people that inhibit it. The island lies in the migratory path of the great Humpback whale, and it is here they come to calve and mate. We are taken on many dives in which the team capture wonderful underwater footage of these gentle giants.

Join the team as they go in search of Snake Gully, the location where sea snakes, indigenous only to the island, come ashore to lay their eggs. It is estimated that around 90% of the hatchlings will be eaten in there first year. Their first test is to make it past the sharks that circle
the island.

Cropp and his team then take us to another part of the island to meet some of the locals to find out more about their culture and their way of life. We find a new church has just been opened, and everyone joins in the celebrations. It is the Niue way to give money and gifts to all the performers at such an event, who perform a dance for all visitors of the island. 

Among the splendid array of scenery and wildlife captured during the filming the team make one last extraordinary discovery when they return to their diving spot to find a baby whale has been born.

n7Jc428GWi0.title: Lagarto à La Bourguignon
n7Jc428GWi0.description:
[INSCREVA-SE no canal e CURTA os vídeos!]... Adaptação ao Boeuf Bourguignon, feito de maneira mais rápida e com produtos que encontramos em todos os hipermercados.

Ingredientes:
- 01 quilo de lagarto
- 150gr de cebolinhas em conserva (na receita vão as cebolinhas, mas, não achei então comprei a que vende em conserva mesmo...rs)
- 100gr de champignon
- 200gr de bacon
- 01 cenoura
- 01 cebola
- 01 dente de alho
- cravos da índia
- Ervas: salsinha, cebolinha, louro, alecrim e hortelã
- 105ml de vinho para tempero (chef Izidro)
- 200ml de vinho tinto
- 1/2 litro de caldo de carne
- Azeite e sal a gosto.
Preparo:
Limpe a carne tirando todo excesso de gordura. Amarre a carne para ela manter o formato. Pegue uma cebola descascada e espete alguns cravos da índia, descasque uma cenoura e corte-a em pedaços (não precisa ser muito pequenos).
Faça um maço de ervas, com salsa, cebolinha, alecrim, louro e hortelã (amarre com um barbante).
Em uma panela grande sele a carne dourando-a de todos os lados em duas colheres de azeite.
Coloque a carne em uma panela de pressão e coloque a cebola, a cenoura, o ramo de ervas, o vinho para tempero e o caldo de carne (eu usei um tablete para 1/2 litro de água).
Deixe cozinhar na pressão por mais ou menos 01 hora (abaixe o fogo quando pegar pressão, não precisa ficar gastando gás e evita da carne pegar no fundo da panela).
Retire a carne da panela e corte em bifes. Coe o molho que ficou na panela (se for preciso acrescente um pouco de água antes de tirar o caldo que ficou na panela)
Pique 200gr de bacon, 100gr de champignon, 01 dente de alho.
Em uma panela grande, coloque o bacon para fritar, deixe dourar e retire (reserve-o) doure as cebolinha em conserva na gordura do bacon (reserve-as), doure o champignon nas mesma panela e reserve.
Volte os ingredientes para a panela e coloque o molho da carne. Acrescente 01 colher de amido de milho dissolvido em 150ml de água (para engrossar o molho).
(Acrescente o vinho tinto se você quiser uma quantidade maior de molho).
Coloque as carnes na panela, mexendo de vez em quando, deixe no fogo por mais 10 minutos.
